# Witty Pi scheduling is disabled by default.
#
# The sculpture remains on continuously while external power is available.
# configure-wittypi.sh removes the installed schedule, clears stored startup
# and shutdown alarms, and configures the Witty Pi hardware for Default ON.
#
# To intentionally restore scheduled power cycling, provide a valid active
# schedule in this file and deploy with ENABLE_WITTYPI_POWER_SCHEDULE=1.
